#. <section class="sutta" id="sn46.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Udāyivagga"
msgstr "3. With Udāyī"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Aparihāniyasutta"
msgstr "25. Non-decline"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.86"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn46.25:1.1"
msgid "“Satta vo, bhikkhave, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you seven principles that guard against decline."

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.2"
msgid "taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the seven principles that guard against decline?"

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.4"
msgid "Yadidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.5"
msgid "satta bojjhaṅgā."
msgstr "They are the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.6"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.7"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr ""
"The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, "
"rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity."

msgctxt "sn46.25:1.8"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, satta aparihāniyā dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the seven principles that guard against decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.25:1.9"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
